  "detailed_description": "Skies Of Blue: Remake is a first-person puzzle-platformer where you work your way through a series of different levels utilizing various key items, including bombs, keys and your pistol, along with fresh and interesting mechanics that change as you progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003690/extras/f564fa7d7481a0382c1be84167db2236.avif?t=1682221780\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Progressive Mechanics</h2>As you progress, new mechanics are added to constantly test you and push your puzzle-solving skills further. That means more ways to play and more ways to fight.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003690/extras/4520f31ecd91b4c6788ec917243f4090.avif?t=1682221780\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bosses</h2><br>Every 20 levels, a powerful boss from the deep depths of the world will cross paths with you and prevent you from progressing further. Take them on and prove your strength and WIN.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003690/extras/82b3c4bf44dd25fab10648b466d83cf7.avif?t=1682221780\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extras</h2>Along with the main gameplay, hidden collectables are hidden around the game, find them all and unlock special abilities to make the gameplay different. Getting bored with playing pre-built levels? The game also contains a custom level builder, so you can make your own levels and show them off to your friends!<br><br><br>There are lots of levels to chose from, with more being added in coming updates.",
  "about_the_game": "Skies Of Blue: Remake is a first-person puzzle-platformer where you work your way through a series of different levels utilizing various key items, including bombs, keys and your pistol, along with fresh and interesting mechanics that change as you progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003690/extras/f564fa7d7481a0382c1be84167db2236.avif?t=1682221780\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Progressive Mechanics</h2>As you progress, new mechanics are added to constantly test you and push your puzzle-solving skills further. That means more ways to play and more ways to fight.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003690/extras/4520f31ecd91b4c6788ec917243f4090.avif?t=1682221780\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bosses</h2><br>Every 20 levels, a powerful boss from the deep depths of the world will cross paths with you and prevent you from progressing further. Take them on and prove your strength and WIN.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003690/extras/82b3c4bf44dd25fab10648b466d83cf7.avif?t=1682221780\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extras</h2>Along with the main gameplay, hidden collectables are hidden around the game, find them all and unlock special abilities to make the gameplay different. Getting bored with playing pre-built levels? The game also contains a custom level builder, so you can make your own levels and show them off to your friends!<br><br><br>There are lots of levels to chose from, with more being added in coming updates.",
